---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Faqs from '../components/home/Faqs.astro';

import faqs from '../data/faqs.json';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | SalesZote" description="Read the SalesZote Privacy Policy to learn how we collect, use, and protect your data.">
    <section class="max-w-8xl mx-auto px-8 xl:px-30 py-20 bg-neutral-50">
        <div class="prose max-w-none">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Privacy Policy – SalesZote</h1>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8"><strong>Effective Date:</strong> 18th August 2025</p>

            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8">
                At SalesZote, we value your trust and are committed to protecting your personal and business information.
                This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you use our platform.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">When you sign up and use SalesZote, we may collect:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-6">
                <li>Personal details such as your name, phone number, and email.</li>
                <li>Business information such as shop/wholesale name, inventory details, and sales records.</li>
                <li>Device and usage data (e.g., IP address, browser type, and how you use our system).</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">We use the information collected to:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-6">
                <li>Provide you with access to your SalesZote dashboard.</li>
                <li>Help you track sales, manage inventory, and generate reports.</li>
                <li>Improve our services and add new features.</li>
                <li>Communicate important updates, offers, or security alerts.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">3. Data Security</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
                We take the security of your information seriously. SalesZote uses encryption, secure servers,
                and other safeguards to protect your data from unauthorized access, loss, or misuse.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">4. Sharing of Information</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information. Your data is only shared in these limited cases:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-6">
                <li>With service providers who help us operate the platform (under strict confidentiality).</li>
                <li>If required by law or government authorities.</li>
                <li>To protect the rights and security of SalesZote, our users, and partners.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">5. Your Rights</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">As a user, you have the right to:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2 mb-6">
                <li>Access and update your personal information.</li>
                <li>Request deletion of your data (subject to legal and business requirements).</li>
                <li>Opt out of marketing communications.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">6. Cookies & Tracking</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
                SalesZote may use cookies and similar technologies to improve user experience and track performance.
                You can manage cookies in your browser settings.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
                We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page
                with an updated effective date.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">8. Contact Us</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
            </p>
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">📧 info@saleszote.com</p>
                <p class="text-gray-700">📞 + 254 701 853 648</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <Faqs faqs={faqs} showContactLink={true} />
</Layout>
